<div1 type="case">

<pb facs="hc.case.0034.010"/>

<p>I bought him as a slave for life if 
I chose to keep him as such - no condi-
tions as to the time he was to serve contained 
in the Bill of Sale</p>

<p>The court adjudjes that Petitioner 
<del>be discharged</del> is illegally restrained 
of his freedom and entitled to be dis-
charged -</p>

<p>Arrested before &amp; committed by Just-
ice Johnson under the afft of John 
Lakin - on 30th June 1858-</p>

</div1>
    
